name: age_group
Note: Probability of meeting someone from the own age group, conditional on meeting someone. Rest of probability mass is split equally across other age groups.

name: region
Note: Probability of meeting someone from the own region conditional on meeting someone. Rest of probability mass is split equally across other regions.

name: cd_infectious_false
Note: This is infectiousness of people who don’t get symptoms

name: cd_symptoms_true
Note: After infectiousness starts, i.e. 6 days after infection takes place

name: cd_knows_true
source: This is the testing lag, might vary by region, inquired from doctor

name: icu_limit_relative
Note: Number of ICU beds, relative to population size
